      "writtenOn": "2018-10-23T20:01:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Moved these to third_party/fuchsia/BUILD.gn.\n\nThis will be exposed in the SDK by https://fuchsia-review.googlesource.com/c/garnet/+/215920, however only the .fidl file is included in the SDK archive. Do you know if it\u0027s possible to generate the FIDL header and sources from the Crashpad standalone build? I am also not sure about the Chromium build case.",
